FBIS4-12991 "drnes073_l_94010" FBIS-NES-94-073 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 ISRAEL Army Urges Residents of Border Area To Go to Shelters Army Urges Residents of Border Area To Go to Shelters NC1504104794 Paris AFP in English 1031 GMT 15 Apr 94 NC1504104794 Paris AFP English BFN [Excerpt] Qiryat Shemona, Israel, April 15 (AFP)--The army on Friday [15 April] urged Israelis living near the border with Lebanon to take shelter for fear of more rocket attacks. Soldiers in vehicles with loudspeakers drove through northern communities urging residents to go down to underground shelters at 1:00 p.m. (1000 GMT), an AFP correspondent said here. [passage omitted]
